@node INTRODUCTION "DigiZ: Introduction"

                               @{u}Introduction@{uu}

    DigiZ is a clock and an alarm clock. But it has something different from others : @{b} It can be opened on any screen@{ub} whereas other clocks can only be opened on the Workbench screen. 

    DigiZ has been created under WB1.2 (which do not know PUBLICSCREENs) but has been finished under WB3.0. It can be run with any system between them.

    @{u}NB@{uu}: You use this program at your own risks...

@endnode

